[I] Library for XMP music players

[T] Libxmp loads the module and renders the sound as linear PCM samples in a
[T] buffer at rate and format specified by the user. Applications for libxmp
[T] include players, module information extractors, module-to-mp3 renderers,
[T] game music, etc. A smaller subset of libxmp is also available. below).

[U] https://xmp.sourceforge.net/

[A] Claudio Matsuoka
